(17,	'THE STUDY OF LAND PARKING  MALL BOGOR INDAH PLAZA  - Syaiful',	'<p>The development of big cities in Indonesia especially the city of Bogor is the density of motor vehicle users. Users of this motor vehicle have a strong impact on the progress of transportation infrastructure. The need for parking is a very valuable resource for the city, especially for the central trading area in the city of Bogor. The increasing number of population and the increase of motor vehicle users, so the comparison between the number of roads, parking lots and parking requirements is not balanced.</p>\r\n',	'2017',	'the-study-of-land-parking-mall-bogor-indah-plaza-syaiful',	'',	'free',	'UIKACOVER_115GROST-00131-TR-Syaiful.pdf',	'Atlantis Pres',	'',	'UIKA',	'JURNAL',	12328,	'2022-10-11 05:45:26'),
(18,	'ROAD MAP KEBISINGAN YANG DITIMBULKAN KENDARAAN BERMOTOR DI KOTA BOGOR  - Syaiful',	'<p>The development of shopping facilities, public spaces and pedestrian, schools hospitals and places of worship and housing is difficult to dammed, these developments are not supported with the addition of roads and road length. Roadmap preparation of research on the noise generated in the motor vehicle and the city of Bogor Regency is to seek and to formulate how much the level of the user INVESTMENTS highway to traffic flow caused by motor vehicles</p>\r\n',	'2014',	'road-map-kebisingan-yang-ditimbulkan-kendaraan-bermotor-di-kota-bogor-syaiful',	'',	'free',	'UIKACOVER_137LPPM-UIKA-2014_SYAIFUL-FINAL PROSIDING-2015.pdf',	'LPPM UIKA',	'',	'UIKA',	'PROSIDING',	12080,	'2022-10-11 07:22:55'),
