ass=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Misi</span></span></b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-top:0cm; margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:6.0pt; text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan yang Islami untuk menghasilkan lulusan yang profesional sesuai kompetensi.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-top:0cm; margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:6.0pt; text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Meningkatkan ilmu pengetahuan, seni dan keterampilan dibidang pendidikan melalui pemanfatan teknologi informasi.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-top:0cm; margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:6.0pt; text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Mengembangkan ilmu pengetahuan melalui penelitian yang inovatif, kreatif dan bermanfaat bagi masyarakat.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-top:0cm; margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:6.0pt; text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Mengembangkan kemitraan dengan lembaga terkait, sebagai bentuk peran serta Fakultas dalam pembangunan masyarakat di tingkat lokal, nasional, regional dan internasional.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-top:0cm; margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:6.0pt; text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Membina civitas akademika menuju terbentuknya pribadi muslim yang beriman, berilmu dan beramal</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Kontak Fakultas</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Telp. 0251 &ndash; 8336325</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Whatsapp : 0812-8484-5913</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Email: fkip@uika-bogor.ac.id</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span calibri=\"\" style=\"font-family:\">Http://fkip.uika-bogor.ac.id</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe allow=\"accelero